These are the total count for the English and Chinese posts:

25Change - is the change over time, week by week, for English Period 1
26Change - is the change over time, week by week, for English Period 2
25diffFull - is the change over time, week by week, for Chinese Period 1
26diffFull - is the change over time, week by week, for Chinese Period 2

The third set of columns in the first sheet of the excel files is the final count of country mentions for each week.
